title: EP 145:  Snowfall Breakdown Pt.1 w/ Glasses Malone
itunes:title: EP 145:  Snowfall Breakdown Pt.1 w/ Glasses Malone
description:
We sat in with Glasses Malone & Peter Bas from No Ceiling's podcast to breakdown the season ending episode of "Snowfall". Glasses say's Leon wont make it to the end, Steele says Jerome will wind up handling Aunt Louie himself, who knows?  

This is Pt. 1 of 2, as me and James do a breakdown in part 2 that drops end of the week.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
